<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5267970>
    dc:description "FIGURE 64. Early stages of Platylesches ayresii on Parinari capensis, South Africa, TCEC. 1, leaf shelter of second instar caterpillar, Krugersdorf, 9 Oct 2010; 2, leaf shelter of pupa, view of the entrance and valve, 12 Dec 2010, Krugersdorp; 3, penultimate instar caterpillar, frontal view of head, 23 Sep 2008, Krugersdorp; 4, caterpillar, frontal view, undated, Krugersdorp; 5, pupa, dorsal view, 1 Oct 2008, Krugersdorp; 6, pupa lateral view, as #4." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5267970/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5267978>
    dc:description "FIGURE 68. Life history of Platylesches langa, collected mostly on Parinari capensis but also on Pa. curatellifolia, Mutinondo Wilderness, Mpika, Zambia, and subsequently reared on Pa. curatellifolia, TCEC. 1, early leaf shelters, 17 Sep 2008; 2, leaf shelter of pupa showing entrance valve, 13 Sep 2010; 3–6, mature caterpillar, 28 Jan 2009: 3, dorsal view; 4, lateral view; 5–6, detail of head, frontal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5267978/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5267966>
    dc:description "FIGURE 62. Heads of final instar caterpillars of the Platylesches iva and Pl. affinissima group, collected on Parinari curatellifolia, Tanzania, TCEC. 1, Pl. sp. close to affinissima, Rondo Plateau, 28 Feb 2007; 2, Pl. sp. close to affinissima, Kihansi Gorge, at the foot of the Udzungwa escarpment, about 350m, 28 Nov 2007; 3–4, Pl. sp. close to iva, Kihansi Gorge, 25 Nov 2007, 22 Feb 2008." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5267966/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5267847>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Leaf shelters of Gorgyra bibulus on Rourea thomsonii, collected 4 Jul 1998, Gatamayu Forest, Kenya; the lines in the background are 8mm apart. 1, stage 1 shelter on left, 98/201E; stage 2 shelter on right, 98/201F; 2, stage 3 shelter, 98/201C; 3, pupal shelter, 98/201A." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5267847/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

